snippet.title: Technobabylon character teaser: Charlie Regis
snippet.description:
Available on Steam and GOG, coming to iPhone/iPad on August 16, 2017

Other character teasers:
Latha Sesame: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x8fkRKoNdso
Max Lao: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6nt6cO4YqRk

Charlie Regis from the upcoming Technobabylon: a cyberpunk adventure game coming this spring from Wadjet Eye Games!
http://www.technobabylon-game.com

Charlie Regis, an agent of the city’s all-seeing secret police, finds himself blackmailed with the lives of his unborn children. Pushed to the limits by his deceit and his past, how far is he willing to go to save his legacy?

Technobabylon developed by: Technocrat Games
Published by: Wadjet Eye Games
Charlie Regis voiced by: Eli Green
Art by: Ben Chandler
Music by: Premium Beats

Follow the development on Twitter with @wadjeteyegames and @technocratgames!

http://www.wadjeteyegames.com
http://www.technocratgames.com
